#

Herb-Crusted Salmon with Lemon Butter Sauce

$18.5
450 kcal

Allergens:

fishdairy

Dietary Tags:

gluten-freehigh-proteinlow-carb

Tags:

gourmetseafooddinnerhealthy

Description

A succulent salmon fillet topped with a flavorful herb crust and drizzled with a zesty lemon butter sauce, perfect for a gourmet dinner.

Ingredients

  • salmon fillet: 2 (6 oz) pieces
  • fresh parsley: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • fresh dill: 2 tablespoons, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • lemon zest: 1 teaspoon
  • butter: 4 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
